data.description: Discover the epitome of comfort in this gorgeous 5-bed, 2.5-bath huge corner lot home boasting a brand-new roof and energy efficient solar panels. Embrace energy efficiency and contemporary living with sleek interiors upgrades, a gourmet kitchen, and a private outdoor oasis with a beautiful pool great for entertaining. This home has a Prime location in the heart of coral springs, Near top-rated schools. There are too many amenities to list. this home won't last!!
